Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:09.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゾルディック家に戻った キルアが その地下深くに幽閉されている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:09.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:40.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや 写真くらい　全然いいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:40.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, what's going on?! Below us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ムーナさん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There was a huge explosion below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アルカとカルトの散歩の途中だし。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Enough waiting around... I'll see what's happening for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　弟です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:48.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Everyone, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕の。 フフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I finally managed to contact the Ten Dons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Please enter the auction hall \Non the tenth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:10.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ。 すごい。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:10.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An underground chamber where everything costs extra.\NThat is where you will sleep. \NNever descend stairs that you didn't first ascend. \NDo not compete with others at numbers. I'll be fine. This is the tenth floor. I'll be safe as long as I don't \Ngo down any stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her fortunes are one hundred \Npercent accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:22.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？ あ　すみませんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:22.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her fortunes won't come true \Nif you heed the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:27.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「おねだり」ごっこなんです。 「ダメよ」って 言ってくれればいいですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:27.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:34.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の代わりに こいつ殺して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:34.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yo, everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}執事のほうは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's been a lot of chaos, but it's all cleared up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:49.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「尻拭い」も執事だったから 犠牲者を追跡しやすかったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:49.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We've dealt with the Phantom Troupe's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}調べてみて あることに気が付いた。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:56.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's only a matter of time before \Nthe rest of them are finished. We're letting the professionals \Nhandle the hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:04:00.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうも　２人が死ぬ場合と 大勢の場合とでは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:04:00.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}so you can enjoy the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:10.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理屈が合わない。 ペアの場合と道連れとでは 犠牲者の選ばれる法則が 違うんじゃないかと。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:10.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tonight, we'll be watching the auction live, so let us see some furious bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:19.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゾルディック家の執事は 敷地内の養成所で教育を受ける。 カスガが死んだ　同日同時刻…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:19.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As you all just heard, the Ten Dons will be watching a \Nlive feed of the proceedings. Please concentrate on the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:05.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}養成所の資料に 「最愛の人は実の母親」とあった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:05.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Illumi? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　実母は　まだ病院で生きてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where is my client? Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:18.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}愛と憎悪は表裏一体さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:18.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, were you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:23.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}賛成だけど この件では少し意見が違う。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:23.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is he still alive? Just in the nick of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実母を嫌いになったんじゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's a relief. Well, relay a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:29.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もっと愛する人ができた…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:29.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've killed the Ten Dons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:34.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カスガには　付き合ったばかりの 恋人がいたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:34.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tell him to wire the money \Nto my account as agreed. Up we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}母親より　さらに短かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good grief. It seems we both get to live another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Aren't you supposed to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}事件後に調べたんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We were hired by the Ten Dons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:51.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}調べた後に事件だろ？ あ　バレた？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:51.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now that they're all dead, you are no longer our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:56.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　そうだよ。 検証に利用した。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:56.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:03.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うちは執事が 恋愛してる時点で死刑だし。 最初の事件で気付いたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:03.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You won't get another chance like this. Do you believe that we kill for pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:07.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつは　相当ヤバい能力だって。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:07.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We don't do this for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:12.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全容を掴んでおかないと ゾルディック家が滅びるほどの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:12.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I refuse to work for nothing \Nor die for nothing. Did you know that I hired Illumi \Nto assassinate the Ten Dons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つ目の事件を 徹底的に調べて　結論が出て
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Of course. But that's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:26.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２つ目で確信した。 アルカからの「おねだり」を ４回失敗すると
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:26.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We simply do the job we're hired for. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}命で償わなければならない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Say, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:37.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}命を失うのが２人の場合 失敗した人と その最愛の人が死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:37.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you and I were to fight one-on-one, who would win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２人よりも犠牲者が多い場合は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Most likely, I would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}失敗した人と その最愛の人はもちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Unless you decided to actually try to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:50.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その２人プラス 失敗した人と長い時間を 共に過ごした人順に死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:50.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Honestly, you're a cheeky kid. So he could tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:14.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアは「ゴンを元通りにして」と アルカに「お願い」する。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:14.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What a drag...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「お願い」をキルア自身がして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I couldn't steal their powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:22.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「尻拭い」を 赤の他人に　なすり付ければ 多分　問題ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:22.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So you want us to wait at L Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:28.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}けど　きっとキルアは 手順を逆にする。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:28.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, it's more dangerous \Nhere than anticipated. We'll send her over by ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お兄ちゃん！ アルカ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But she'll be much safer at a hospital. Make the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:46.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアは 誰かに「お願い」してもらって 「尻拭い」を 自分でしようとするだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:46.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Looks like you had fun, boss... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ごめんな　アルカ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm a little tired now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:54.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こんなとこに ずっと　ほっといて…　ごめんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:54.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You were up against the Zoldyck family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいの！　うれしい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wish I could've seen how \Nthose two fought you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:01.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ　お兄ちゃんの匂いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:01.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fighting would be more fun than watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:12.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネテロが「薔薇」を 使わざるを得ないほどの怪物。 その側近を倒すため
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:12.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kortopi, everything ready? Of course. I can't make living copies, but I can provide static copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:16.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンは自分自身に ある意味　死よりも重い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:16.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good enough. Then we'll stick to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:22.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「誓約と制約」を念じたんだろう。 それを元通りにしてという 「お願い」は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:22.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Also... Don't touch the ambulance that girl is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:29.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}金や医学のレベルを はるかに超えている。 恐らく　「お願い」は叶う。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:29.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will we really be safe on the trip over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:33.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　キルアは命懸けで アルカの「おねだり」を聞く。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:33.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If they planned to attack the ambulance, \Nthey would've done so on its way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでもキルアは聞こうとして 途中で力尽きる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the moment you've all been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ミッション失敗。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We will now begin the auction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:54.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最愛の者と　長く共にいた者。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:54.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Allow me to introduce our \Nfirst item of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:59.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どちらだとしても 元通りになったゴンも死ぬ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:59.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was concerned for a moment. But all's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:05.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？ えっ？ あぁ…。 違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:05.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And none of the leaders were hurt. We did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:11.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしかして 前に言った　「２人とも」って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:11.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:29.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕も大慨だけど　君も相当だな。 っていうか手順を間違ったら キルアと俺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:29.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Allow me to introduce the next item.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:35.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…と　ゴンだけじゃなくて ゾルディックの人間 みんな死んじゃうんだけどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:35.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An executioner's blade made of pure gold, taken from the Yulu Museum \Nof National Treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何より　僕は この「お願い」の道連れは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's start the bidding at 20 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}万単位だと思ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}40 million! 50 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:44.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}多分　ヒソカも死ぬよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:44.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hear 50 million... 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「えっ？」って言ったのは そういうこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll put him on autopilot now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ　困るね。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Next, we have the fabled \Nsacred jar of the Rai Dynasty, Inspirational Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お兄ちゃん　死んで。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Um, Inspirational Blue is... Over here. Kortopi, this one is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　いいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here, make a copy. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:20.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺がキルアに　正しい手順で 「お願い」するように頼むから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:20.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gallery Fake: Divine Left Hand, \NDemonic Right Hand Here comes Inspirational Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:26.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その場に隠れて立ち会ってくれ。 キルアが　「嫌だ」と言った場合と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:26.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's start the bidding at 100 million! 200 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:32.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「いいよ」と言っていても ウソをついていると 判断できた場合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:32.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}330 million! 380 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アルカを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}始末してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Aren't you going to participate \Nin the auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:43.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}普通の子供だと思っていい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:43.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The leader of the Troupe was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:46.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハ　アハハハ　ハハっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:46.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why wouldn't they proceed? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:50.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ただ どこから来たかが分からない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:50.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It can't be... We're just mopping up leftovers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:04.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}欠席６８票。 投票率８９．７％。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:04.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}While your useless ass was busy \Nfussing over an ambulance, the Zoldycks got the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:13.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２回目の欠席は３３票で 今回は６８票。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:13.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So you're not needed any longer. Just stick with your little fortune girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:20.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}棄権が増えましたねぇ。 これ　前回は無効票だった人達が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:20.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Run off to the hospital or the hotel. Or will you lick the boots
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:27.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今回は無効にできないから ライセンスの没収覚悟で 投票に来なかった ってことですよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:27.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}of that old fraud who \Nfailed to score any points—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:34.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ　そいつらは そこまでするんだ！ それじゃあ　二重の違反者は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:34.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I won't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ライセンスの没収を 実行していいですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Not until I see a body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その人達への文書に２点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本部へ ライセンスを持参すること
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's young. Cocky son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:55.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その際　棄権の理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:55.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, don't touch his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:59.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}明確に説明してもらう旨を 明記してください。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:59.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're going to show his \Nface on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　どうでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We found the other members' bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それだけで 本当に大丈夫ですかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, I'm on my way. A total of five bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:10.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}違反者はライセンスの代わりに 免罪符を得たんですよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:10.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Try to identify them. DNA, teeth, fingerprints, disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:15.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「もうこれで　何度　棄権しても 怖いものはない」っていうね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:15.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Try everything you can! You can dismember them, \Nbut don't touch the heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:24.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言い出したのは　てめぇだろうが！ 没収の件はよ！ あれ？ でも　最終的には多数決ですよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:24.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once we have their identities, we'll kill their parents, siblings, \Nrelatives, and lovers! We'll make sure no one ever
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それに　資格の期限付き失効は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}tries a stunt like this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}賛成してましたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:44.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう… こいつが　とても嫌なのは 自身が不利になりそうな提案を すんなり受け入れたり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:44.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's time for our last item tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:47.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分から 言い出したりもするところ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:47.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One of the world's seven \Nmost beautiful items, the Scarlet Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:53.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まるで邪魔や障害を 楽しんでいる節さえある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:53.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}With the Kurta Clan's extinction, only thirty-six pairs exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんなとこだけ ネテロ会長に似てる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This particular set has a \Nparticularly brilliant red hue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが　とても嫌！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, let's start the bidding at 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そこで　提案します。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}110 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:08.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「十二支ん」全員で 演説しましょうよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:08.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}120 million! 130 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハンター会員　みんなの前で。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}150 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この選挙が　いかに大事か。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Boss? It's Kurapika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:18.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}協会のために　人類のために 世界のために！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:18.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I apologize. I predicted incorrectly. The leader of the spiders is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネットの画面なんて 通しちゃダメなんですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The auction is proceeding as scheduled. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一人一人の目を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Scarlet Eyes are currently \Nbeing auctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生の声を 生の魂にぶつけるんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:28.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should I bid on them? Of course! You must win them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}前会長のためにも！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is there a limit as to price?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:34.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こんなところが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:34.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No! Bid as much as it takes! Win the Scarlet Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬほど嫌いよ　パリストン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I understand. 300 million! I hear 300 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:45.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お兄ちゃん　起きて！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:45.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyone else? Do I have any more bids? 350 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ばぁ！ アハハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}1 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:04.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アルカには　いくつか 親父達は知らないルールがある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:04.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2.9 b-billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:11.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お兄ちゃん　しり取りしよ。 ああ　いいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:11.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, the skinhead who was in the \Nroom with the assassins put up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:15.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあね　うん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:15.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Zenji? Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アルカの「ア」！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't expect to spend \Nthis much, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:21.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「お兄ちゃん」と俺を呼ぶのは 本当のアルカ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:21.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Curse that pig. No matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:27.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「キルア」と呼ぶのは 別のナニカ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:27.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This means that the community \Nreceives more money, which will benefit my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is an investment in my trek to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:10.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアったら すっかり　お兄ちゃんになって。 これで３回　「おねだり」クリアだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:10.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can throw money at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're from the Nostrade Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ！　ご…　ごめんよ　パパ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is this the item you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　しないから！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だからアルカは　執事に １個　「おねだり」させてから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:11.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パパとママの所に戻すように 俺が仕組んでた。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:11.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You think you can just walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:15.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアも　そうしてたと思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:15.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tsk... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アルカが　パパとママに 「おねだり」しなかったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll blow your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そのためだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:26.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３　「おねだり」されている誰かが 途中で死ぬと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:26.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't be... Just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:32.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「おねだり」は失敗と見なされて 最低でも　もう一人　死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:32.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't care who I kill right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:38.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは　実験して確認済み。 ４　アルカが 名前を知らない人物には
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:38.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even if it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}また何か 甘いこと考えてんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, I'm getting into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアが　ここで「お願い」したら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How about another? Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:18.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その「尻拭い」は 他の誰かがやるわけだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:18.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They were drinking while \Nwe were captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}考えられぬ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, you're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:26.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず友達を助けてから 考えればいいことではないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:26.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come and drink with us! Are you an idiot? We're underage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パパ。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And aren't you underage too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見知らぬ その他大勢を犠牲にして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}助けられた友人は　それを喜ぶか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In my country, you can drink \Nonce you're sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}否！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…とか考えちゃうんだよ あいつは。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I had no idea that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達とは 思考が　かなり　ずれてるからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm amazed you escaped alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:49.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　イル兄に 針で矯正させてたんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:49.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Phantom Troupe's that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？ はっ…。 動いた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Back there, one of the tricks \Nyou taught us came in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}親父　開けてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Make your own! I get it. I'm glad I was able to help in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前達を外に出すことはできない。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Experience can sometimes blind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A con artist's knowledge might come \Nin handy against the Troupe. Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:26.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どのルールも 親父達は知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:26.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's more to being a con \Nartist than you'd think. I haven't just been drinking \Nmyself senseless here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}親父…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've been learning a lot from Zepile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達　やっぱり親子だね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And tomorrow morning, \Nwe'll hit the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　別のどこかから来た闇…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd like to, but I have to find Kurapika \Nand learn about Nen from him. Kurapika? You got through to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　そう言ったよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yep, but we're waiting for \Nhim to call us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:51.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　俺も 実は　黒目の時のこいつを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:51.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hold on. Did you say you need to learn \Nabout Nen from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナニカって呼んでるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I did. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:19:02.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　俺達　行くよ。 俺の「尻拭い」は　俺がする。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:19:02.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He just learned about Nen \Nrecently himself, right? But Kurapika managed to defeat a \Nmember of the Phantom Troupe. Seriously? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナニカ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He must know some secret about Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:14.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３０分以内に　この山から俺達が 一緒に出られなかったら 母親を…　殺せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:14.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Some strength that doesn't \Nrequire experience or power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:29.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３０分以内に俺達２人が 一緒に山を下りられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:29.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you feeling better now? Uh-huh, I forgive you! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:33.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺のほっぺにチューしろ 分かったな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:33.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:44.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…　あああ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:44.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My daughter is doing well, so we'll head back to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ママ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tomorrow, we need to buy \Nthe actor's used tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:20:04.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア…。 何て…　何て残酷なことを 言えるようになったの。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:20:04.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I want you to accompany \Nmy daughter as she shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:16.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソっ！ こんなやり方もできたのか！ 結果的に 叶う「お願い」が１つなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:16.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kurapika... We can handle the remainder \Nof the auction and shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:19.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}選択を迫れるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:19.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:25.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TV]　親父…　開けてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:25.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thanks, I think I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナニカは　壊すのは得意だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That won't be necessary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}直すのは苦手だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The spider is dead. Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:06.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}直す時は 実際に触らないと力が出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:06.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kurapika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Mafia community was nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ！　フフっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We didn't even need Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:48.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((３０分以内に俺達２人が 一緒に山を下りられたら 俺のほっぺにチューしろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:48.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kurapika is now drowning in \Nan indescribable emptiness.
